==English==
===Noun===
'''dividend''' (''plural'' '''dividends''')

#{{arithmetic}} A number or [[expression]] that is to be divided by another.  Eg. in "42 ÷ 3" the dividend is the 42.
#{{finance}} A payment of money by a [[company]] to its [[shareholder]]s, usually made periodically (eg. [[quarterly]] or [[half yearly]]) but at the discretion of the [[board of directors]].

